 <H1>Policies: Implementation</H1> 
 <P><UL></P>

<P><LI><H2>Trusting someone to drive a car:
</H2></P>

<P><UL></P>

<P><LI>By identity: a list of authorized drivers
<LI>By object: a set of keys to be handed out
<LI>By capability: rent a car with license & insurance
</UL></UL><UL></P>

<P><LI><H2>Choice of �primary axis� depends on:
</H2></P>

<P><UL></P>

<P><LI>Simplicity: which is the smallest set?	bank employees
<LI>Dynamism: avoid enumerating the volatile. 	drivers
<LI>Efficiency: what�s easiest to check?	Licenses
</UL></UL><UL></P>

<P><LI><H2>Watch for conflicting policy styles
</H2></P>

<P><UL></P>

<P><LI>Hotel erred in using payment-ability as identity</UL></UL></P>

